{"type": "article", "id": 9886, "title": "Honeycomb Gloss Adidas 女鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-22T07:26:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135138zVYAuragd0pWoHQb.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAdidas Originals 最近以其经典小白鞋 Stan Smith 为蓝本，新推出了一个叫做 Honeycomb Gloss 的女鞋系列。这一系列作品保留了 Stan Smith 经典的样式，包括简单的轮廓和配色。而不同的是，在材料上这次选用带有蜂窝纹路细节的白色皮革，而不是原来光滑的皮革，看上去细节充实。这个系列产品将于今年 6 月 1 日正式登陆 Adidas Originals 店铺。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135136XYBx6wTidHZbUtKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061351376fKSLeTV4NUv7CdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135137DBKxX0RTUewPniOh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}